Review: Amazing food! One of the best XLBs I’ve had in a while and their string beans are to die for! Super crunchy and full of garlic, which I love :) the drinks are quite good too! I would definitely recommend the lychee martini! Bumping off one star because the wait can be long if you don’t have a reservation

Extremely overpriced but one of the best brown sugar milk teas I’ve had in a while! Definitely get it 50% or less for the sweetness as it can be quite sweet. The creamy consistency is absolutely perfect
